(5819,'en','default','1273e64fbdc1cd7c1fac83afa38a0062','The Cron API has been updated with new functions to assist with returning data and includes new filters for modifying cron storage. Other changes in behavior affect cron spawning on servers running FastCGI and PHP-FPM versions 7.0.16 and above.',NULL,NULL,'LINE',NULL,0,'','3f829cfb6e173002070f28b50c89ddfe','',NULL),
