ta\";s:17:\"themes for hotels\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"wordpress themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"wordpress themes for hotels\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=232312\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:604:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WordPress themes for hotels and resorts? A hotel or resort theme must have all the features that help you showcase your properties and also allows travelers to easily book a room. You need to look for a theme that covers all the important features like online booking, room selection, [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-themes-for-hotels/\">29 Best WordPress Themes for Hotels &#038; Resorts (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37938:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WordPress themes for hotels and resorts? </p>\n<p>A hotel or resort theme must have all the features that help you showcase your properties and also allows travelers to easily book a room. You need to look for a theme that covers all the important features like online booking, room selection, etc.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share some of the best WordPress themes for hotels and resorts.</p>\n<h3>Choosing a WordPress Hotel Theme for Your Site</h3>\n<p>Not every WordPress hotel theme is created equal. </p>\n<p>Before you dive in and choose a theme, you need to ensure the theme has certain features:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Showcase your properties and amenities to potential renters</li>\n<li>An optimal location for placing a booking form</li>\n<li>Compatible with the plugins that you want to use, especially the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-booking-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Booking Plugins Compared\">booking form plugin</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Let&#8217;s take a look at some of the best WordPress themes for hotels and resorts.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" title=\"Astra Theme\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">1. Astra Theme</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" title=\"Astra Theme\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/astratheme.jpg\" alt=\"Astra Theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232342\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/astratheme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/astratheme-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/astratheme-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Astra is a lightweight and modern WordPress theme. It has multiple starter sites including a demo website for hotels, resorts, B&#038;Bs, and hostels. This theme is compatible with all the popular <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\" title=\"7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders Compared\">drag and drop page builders</a> that help you design your landing pages.</p>\n<p>It comes with an image gallery to display the photos of your hotel rooms. Astra is easy to set up and optimized to perform faster than regular WordPress themes.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oceanwp/\" title=\"OceanWP\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">2. OceanWP</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oceanwp/\" title=\"OceanWP\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/oceanwp-1.jpg\" alt=\"OceanWP\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232341\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/oceanwp-1.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/oceanwp-1-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/oceanwp-1-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>OceanWP is a free and all-purpose WordPress theme designed to create any type of website. It comes with a demo site for hotels and resorts that you can quickly import on your site with a click. Ocean WP features multiple sections on the homepage including welcome, about us, services, and more. It allows you to add a custom logo, simple navigation menu, and full-width image with CTA in the header section.</p>\n<p>This theme is 100% responsive and it fully <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-compared/\" title=\"6 BEST WordPress eCommerce Plugins Compared\">supports eCommerce</a>. OceanWP is translation ready and can be used for creating RTL (Right to Left) websites. For additional features, you can use their premium extensions and addons.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-sunresort/\" title=\"Sun Resort\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">3. Sun Resort</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-sunresort/\" title=\"Sun Resort\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/sunresort.jpg\" alt=\"Sun Resort\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232343\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/sunresort.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/sunresort-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/sunresort-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Sun Resort is a stylish WordPress theme for hotels and resorts websites. It has a built-in booking request form that helps users book accommodation in your hotel or resort. It comes with a drag and drop homepage builder to add your content instantly.</p>\n<p>Other significant features include custom widgets, color schemes, 1-click demo import, and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-seo-tools-to-grow-your-site-traffic/\" title=\"9 Best SEO Tools to Grow Your Website Traffic, FAST!\">SEO optimization</a>. Sun Resort theme is super flexible and is easy to set up.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-essence-pro/\" title=\"Essence\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">4. Essence</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-essence-pro/\" title=\"Essence\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/essence.jpg\" alt=\"Essence\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232344\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/essence.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/essence-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/essence-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Essence is a powerful WordPress theme that can be used to create a hotel or resort website. It has a full-width background image holding the custom logo, navigation menu, search bar, welcome message, and subscription form. It comes with a simple design to showcase your featured content beautifully.</p>\n<p>This theme is Gutenberg optimized, meaning you can publish content right from the latest WordPress editor, Gutenberg without hassle. It&#8217;s built on top of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-genesis/\" title=\"Genesis Framework\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Genesis framework</a>, one of the most popular premium WordPress theme frameworks available on the market. It&#8217;s bundled with an easy-to-use theme options panel for easy theme setup. Essence offers 6 widget areas that help you quickly add features on the homepage and other pages.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/hermesthemes-bordeaux/\" title=\"Bordeaux\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">5. Bordeaux</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/hermesthemes-bordeaux/\" title=\"Bordeaux\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/bordeaux.jpg\" alt=\"Bordeaux\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232345\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/bordeaux.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/bordeaux-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/bordeaux-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Bordeaux is a bold WordPress theme for boutique hotels and B&#038;Bs. It allows you to add online booking feature on your website, so the travelers can book hotel rooms easily. It comes with a homepage slideshow to display hotel images, room images, and more photos.</p>\n<p>Bordeaux can be fully customized for colors, branding, and typography. This theme is beginner friendly and can be customized using the live WordPress customizer.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-santorini-resort/\" title=\"Santorini Resort\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">6. Santorini Resort</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-santorini-resort/\" title=\"Santorini Resort\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/santorini.jpg\" alt=\"Santorini\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232346\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/santorini.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/santorini-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/santorini-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Santorini Resort is a beautiful WordPress theme built specifically for creating a hotel or resort website. It has a unique design with a full-width custom background image. It comes with an <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-booking-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Booking Plugins Compared\">online booking form</a> for users to book rooms.</p>\n<p>This theme has 7 content types, flexible homepage sections, custom widgets, and more. It&#8217;s optimized for SEO and performance.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/hermesthemes-arcadia/\" title=\"Arcadia\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">7. Arcadia</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/hermesthemes-arcadia/\" title=\"Arcadia\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/arcadia.jpg\" alt=\"Arcadia\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232347\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/arcadia.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/arcadia-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/arcadia-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Arcadia is a professional WordPress hotel and resort theme. It has amazing custom features like background image, headers, fullscreen image slider, and more. It includes a booking form template, social media icons, and multiple page templates.</p>\n<p>It can be customized using the WordPress customizer with live preview. You can change almost everything in the theme to get your desired hotel website up and running.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-sixtyone/\" title=\"SixtyOne\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">8. SixtyOne</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-sixtyone/\" title=\"SixtyOne\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/sixtyone.jpg\" alt=\"SixtyOne\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232348\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/sixtyone.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/sixtyone-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/sixtyone-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>SixtyOne is a modern WordPress theme designed for hotels and accommodation businesses. Like other popular WordPress hotel themes, it includes an online booking form for travelers to book rooms in your hotel. It comes with <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-gallery-plugins-compared/\" title=\"8 Best WordPress Gallery Plugins Compared\">image galleries</a> and hotel management system.</p>\n<p>It features custom widgets, page templates, location maps, and landing pages. This theme is easy to set up and performs well on all screen sizes.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-hotelia/\" title=\"Hotelia\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">9. Hotelia</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-hotelia/\" title=\"Hotelia\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelia.jpg\" alt=\"Hotelia\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232349\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelia.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelia-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelia-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>As the name suggests, Hotelia is specifically created for building a hotel website. It has an elegant and robust design with advanced features like online booking, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-slider-plugins-comparison/\" title=\"12 Best WordPress Slider Plugins (Compared)\">image slider</a>, page builder, parallax effects, and more. It comes with a video background, sticky navigation, custom logo, and premium plugins.</p>\n<p>It also includes custom fonts, post types, widgets, colors, and more. Hotelia is beginner friendly and provides you with extensive documentation that guides you with every aspect of setting up a site with it.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-palermo/\" title=\"Palermo\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">10. Palermo</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-palermo/\" title=\"Palermo\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/palermo.jpg\" alt=\"Palermo\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232350\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/palermo.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/palermo-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/palermo-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Palermo is a beautiful WordPress hotel and resorts theme. It has a sidebar navigation menu with a custom logo and bold background. It displays a fullscreen image background on the right side of the screen. You can add a welcome message and a call-to-action button to the homepage.</p>\n<p>This theme has over 30 appearance options and combinations It also has a 1-click demo import tool and is highly optimized for site speed.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/enginethemes-hotelengine-classy/\" title=\"HotelEngine Classy\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">11. HotelEngine Classy</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/enginethemes-hotelengine-classy/\" title=\"HotelEngine Classy\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelengine.jpg\" alt=\"HotelEngine Classy\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232351\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelengine.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelengine-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelengine-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>HotelEngine Classy is a WordPress theme made for the hostels, resorts, boutique hotels, and accommodation businesses. It&#8217;s bundled with a fullscreen image slider on the homepage carrying your logo, navigation menu, and online <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/make-appointment-booking-system-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Make an Appointment Booking System with WordPress\">reservation form</a>.</p>\n<p>On the homepage, you can display hotel rooms with amenities, customer testimonials, location, and image gallery. Although it has a custom made theme options panel, you can customize it with the live WordPress customizer as well.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-kea/\" title=\"Kea\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">12. Kea</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-kea/\" title=\"Kea\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/kea.jpg\" alt=\"Kea\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232352\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/kea.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/kea-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/kea-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Kea is a minimalistic WordPress resort theme that can be used to create hotel and resort websites. It allows you to integrate your own booking system using a WordPress <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-booking-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Booking Plugins Compared\">booking plugin</a>. It gives a beautiful first impression with the video and image slider on the homepage.</p>\n<p>This theme has flexible layouts, multiple color choices, and WPML support to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/easily-create-multilingual-wordpress-website/\" title=\"How to Easily Create a Multilingual WordPress Website (Step by Step)\">create a multilingual website</a>. It also uses custom Elementor widgets to design your own pages.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/enginethemes-hotelengine-comfy/\" title=\"HotelEngine Comfy\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">13. HotelEngine Comfy</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/enginethemes-hotelengine-comfy/\" title=\"HotelEngine Comfy\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelenginecomfy.jpg\" alt=\"HotelEngine Comfy\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232353\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelenginecomfy.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelenginecomfy-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelenginecomfy-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>HotelEngine Comfy is a beautifully designed WordPress theme for hotels and resorts. It ships with image galleries and sliders to showcase your hotel rooms, lobbies, and pathways. The theme has a professional hotel management system and online booking form.</p>\n<p>It comes with a powerful search engine, colors, fonts, and more custom options. This theme is easy to set up and allows you to start a hotel website instantly.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-milos/\" title=\"Milos\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">14. Milos</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-milos/\" title=\"Milos\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/milos.jpg\" alt=\"Milos\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232354\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/milos.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/milos-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/milos-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Milos is a premium WordPress theme built for hotels, hostels, apartment rentals, B&#038;Bs, and hospitality businesses. It comes with a fullscreen background image below the header. The header includes a custom logo and navigation menu. You can also add a booking button in the header.</p>\n<p>It allows you to integrate third-party booking and reservation system. The theme gives you complete control of the colors. It&#8217;s simple and beginner friendly to set up.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-locales/\" title=\"Locales\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">15. Locales</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-locales/\" title=\"Locales\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/locales.jpg\" alt=\"Locales\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232355\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/locales.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/locales-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/locales-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Locales is a modern WordPress directory theme that helps you create a directory of local hotels. It&#8217;s packed with supportive features like location maps, addresses, and more. You can also add filterable search on the homepage to let the users find the best hotel in town.</p>\n<p>It allows you to display hotels and apartments in a carousel slider. It has a homepage section to display featured hotels. The theme is perfect to showcase the hotels of your town and earn a commission on bookings.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/hermesthemes-prestige/\" title=\"Prestige\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">16. Prestige</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/hermesthemes-prestige/\" title=\"Prestige\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/prestige.jpg\" alt=\"Prestige\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232356\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/prestige.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/prestige-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/prestige-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Prestige is a beautifully crafted WordPress hotel theme. It has multiple page templates to display your rooms, room types, and more. It allows you to showcase nearby attractions that can develop an interest in the user to book a room at your hotel.</p>\n<p>This theme is easy to set up and can be customized using the WordPress theme customizer with live preview.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-moliere/\" title=\"Moliere\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">17. Moliere</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-moliere/\" title=\"Moliere\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/moliere.jpg\" alt=\"Moliere\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232357\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/moliere.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/moliere-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/moliere-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Moliere is an excellent WordPress theme for hotels, resorts, rental apartments, and B&#038;Bs. It comes with a flexible header and footer that allows you to customize each element on the website. It gives you the control on color schemes to define your own colors.</p>\n<p>Other significant features include Google fonts integration and support for <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\" title=\"7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders\">page builders</a>, WooCommerce, and RTL languages.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/templatic-hotelbooking/\" title=\"HotelBooking\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">18. HotelBooking</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/templatic-hotelbooking/\" title=\"HotelBooking\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelbooking.jpg\" alt=\"HotelBooking\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232358\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelbooking.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelbooking-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelbooking-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>HotelBooking is a fully functional WordPress hotel theme. It has a responsive design and hotel reservation system. This theme comes with a booking engine that allows your users to quickly book rooms in your hotel. You can add a customizable booking form, room availability calendar, discount coupons, and more.</p>\n<p>This theme gives you the option to add seasonal rates for rooms. It has a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-start-a-blog-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Start a WordPress Blog (&#038; Make Extra Income)\">separate blog page</a> to post content about your hotel.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/hotelone/\" title=\"Hotelone\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">19. Hotelone</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/hotelone/\" title=\"Hotelone\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelone.jpg\" alt=\"Hotelone\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232359\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelone.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelone-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelone-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Hotelone is a free WordPress theme for hotels and resorts. It comes with an advanced admin panel to customize all elements of the theme. It ships with a pre-built layout for your hotel website making it easier to get started. It has a widgetized footer to add social media icons, services, and more at the bottom of your site. You can also add a travel map, location, and address in the footer. This theme supports the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/elementor-pro/\" title=\"Elementor\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Elementor builder</a> to design your pages.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-philoxenia/\" title=\"Philoxenia\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">20. Philoxenia</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-philoxenia/\" title=\"Philoxenia\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/philoxenia.jpg\" alt=\"Philoxenia\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232360\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/philoxenia.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/philoxenia-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/philoxenia-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Philoxenia is a beautiful and modern WordPress hotel theme. It has all the features you need in your hotel website including a booking form, multiple content types, image gallery to showcase hotel rooms, and a room management system.</p>\n<p>This theme offers widgetized homepage, custom widgets, and color schemes to set up your website. It&#8217;s highly optimized for SEO.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/hotel-luxury/\" title=\"Hotel Luxury\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">21. Hotel Luxury</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/hotel-luxury/\" title=\"Hotel Luxury\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelluxury.jpg\" alt=\"Hotel Luxury\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232361\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelluxury.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelluxury-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelluxury-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Hotel Luxury is another free WordPress hotel theme. It allows you to manage your online bookings and reservations in a professional way. It has a beautiful design to display your hotel accommodations in style. This theme is easy to set up and can be customized with the live WordPress customizer.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/hotelica/\" title=\"Hotelica\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">22. Hotelica</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/hotelica/\" title=\"Hotelica\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelica.jpg\" alt=\"Hotelica\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232362\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelica.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelica-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelica-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Hotelica is a free WordPress theme designed specifically for hotels, resorts, and hospitality businesses. It has a full-width header background image with custom logo, welcome tagline, and navigation menu. You can use this theme to create a local hotels directory. This theme can be customized using the WordPress customizer with live preview.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-zermatt/\" title=\"Zermatt\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">23. Zermatt</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-zermatt/\" title=\"Zermatt\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/zermatt.jpg\" alt=\"Zermatt\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232363\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/zermatt.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/zermatt-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/zermatt-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Zermatt is a highly advanced and flexible WordPress theme for hotels, resorts, rental apartments, B&#038;Bs, hostels, and accommodation businesses. It features attractive fullscreen backgrounds to create a powerful first impression on the users. The theme features include online booking form, weather module, and CTAs.</p>\n<p>It comes with endless color possibilities, fully customizable layouts, page builders, and WooCommerce support. Zermatt is easy to set up and optimized for speed.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-presence/\" title=\"Presence\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">24. Presence</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-presence/\" title=\"Presence\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/presence.jpg\" alt=\"Presence\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232364\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/presence.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/presence-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/presence-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Prestige is a modern <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-multi-purpose-themes/\" title=\"25 Best WordPress Multi-Purpose Themes\">WordPress multi-purpose theme</a>. It can be used to create a hotel or resort website easily. It uses the drag and drop page builders to design <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-landing-page-plugins/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Landing Page Plugins That Convert\">landing pages</a>. This theme includes 2 layouts to either create a boxed or full-width website.</p>\n<p>With built-in website demos, you can get started real quick and launch your hotel website. The theme setup is simple and can be customized with live WordPress customizer.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-olympus-inn/\" title=\"Olympus Inn\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">25. Olympus Inn</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-olympus-inn/\" title=\"Olympus Inn\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/olympusinn.jpg\" alt=\"Olympus Inn\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232365\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/olympusinn.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/olympusinn-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/olympusinn-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Olympus Inn is a stylish WordPress theme for hotels, hospitality businesses, accommodations, and resorts. Like all the popular themes in this list, it has an online reservation form. This theme works great with all the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/top-wordpress-plugins/\" title=\"27 Best WordPress Plugins that You MUST Use\">must have WordPress plugins</a> to add features and functionalities to your hotel website.</p>\n<p>It supports page builders, WooCommerce, RTL languages, and is fully <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/seo-friendly/\" title=\"How to Make Your WordPress Site SEO Friendly\">optimized for SEO</a>. Olympus Inn performs faster than other regular WordPress themes.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-aegean/\" title=\"Aegean Resort\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">26. Aegean Resort</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-aegean/\" title=\"Aegean Resort\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/aegeanresort.jpg\" alt=\"Aegean Resort\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232337\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/aegeanresort.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/aegeanresort-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/aegeanresort-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for a beautiful and modern WordPress resort theme, then check out Aegean Resort. It comes with all the amazing features you need to build a hotel or resort website. The most notable features are weather module, online booking form, image galleries, sliders, and background videos.</p>\n<p>This theme is <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpml/\" title=\"WPML\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">WPML</a> compatible which means you can easily create a multilingual website. It has flexible layout options to design your homepage and landing pages.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-flat/\" title=\"Flat\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">27. Flat</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-flat/\" title=\"Flat\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/flat.jpg\" alt=\"Flat\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232338\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/flat.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/flat-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/flat-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Flat is a professional multipurpose WordPress theme that can be used to create a hotel or resort website. It has a unique flat layout with bold colors and fully customizable to add effects, animations, and more. It comes with <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-builder/\" title=\"Themify Builder\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Themify builder</a> to design your own pages.</p>\n<p>The theme has homepage sections to display your hotel rooms, customer testimonials, staff members, and amenities. It&#8217;s easy to set up and can be customized with the live WordPress customizer.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/hotel-melbourne/\" title=\"Hotel Melbourne\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">28. Hotel Melbourne</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/hotel-melbourne/\" title=\"Hotel Melbourne\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelmelbourne.jpg\" alt=\"Hotel Melbourne\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232339\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelmelbourne.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelmelbourne-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelmelbourne-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Hotel Melbourne is a free and responsive WordPress theme for hotels, resorts, and luxury rental apartments. It has multiple navigation menu locations, image slider, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-social-media-plugins/\" title=\"12 Best WordPress Social Media Plugins\">social media integration</a>, and more. It comes with hotel booking facilities, room management, and more premium features in their paid version.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-hotelmotel/\" title=\"HotelMotel\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">29. HotelMotel</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-hotelmotel/\" title=\"HotelMotel\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelmotel.jpg\" alt=\"HotelMotel\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232340\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelmotel.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelmotel-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/hotelmotel-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>HotelMotel is a premium WordPress hotel theme. It has a reservation system, room management, blog, and Instagram widget. It comes with an image slider to showcase your hotel facilities and nearby attractions. This theme is fully customizable and easy to set up.</p>\n<p>It ships with custom colors, widgets, fonts, and more. The theme has support for WooCommerce and translation ready to let you create a website in your own language.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find the best WordPress themes for hotels and resorts. You may also want to check out our guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-themes-for-travel-blogs/\" title=\"27 Best WordPress Themes for Travel Blogs\">best WordPress themes for travel blogs</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-themes-for-hotels/\">29 Best WordPress Themes for Hotels &#038; Resorts (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-themes-for-hotels/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"Smart Slider 3 Review (2019): Is It Better Than Soliloquy?\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/smart-slider-3/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/smart-slider-3/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 04 Jun 2019 10:11:18 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?post_type=isitwp_plugin&p=233869\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:578:\"<p>Looking for a slider plugin for your WordPress site? Want to know if Smart Slider 3 is the right slider plugin for you? In our Smart Slider 3 review, we’ll take a look at its features and help you decide if it’s the best slider plugin for your needs and budget. About Smart Slider 3 [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/smart-slider-3/\">Smart Slider 3 Review (2019): Is It Better Than Soliloquy?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Shahzad Saeed\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11341:\"<p>Looking for a slider plugin for your WordPress site? Want to know if Smart Slider 3 is the right slider plugin for you? In our Smart Slider 3 review, we’ll take a look at its features and help you decide if it’s the best slider plugin for your needs and budget.</p>\n<h3>About Smart Slider 3</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/smart-slider-3/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/smart-slider-3-review-1.png\" alt=\"smart slider 3 review\" width=\"740\" height=\"236\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233875\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/smart-slider-3-review-1.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/smart-slider-3-review-1-300x96.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/smart-slider-3/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Smart Slider 3</a> is one of the most powerful and easy-to-use <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-slider-plugins-comparison/\">slider plugins</a> for your WordPress site. It’s released by Nextend, a team from Hungary that sells premium-quality software for WordPress and Joomla.</p>\n<p>Smart Slider 3 is a freemium plugin with 400,000+ active installs for their free version. Its free version provides more features than any other plugin in the WordPress repository. With the pro version, you get updates for lifetime and hundreds of sample sliders.</p>\n<h3>Smart Slider 3 Review: Tons of Templates With Easy-to-use Interface</h3>\n<p>The best thing about <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/smart-slider-3/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Smart Slider 3</a> is that even if you’re an absolute beginner, you can build a stunning slider with ease.</p>\n<p>Unlike most slider plugins, the interface is NOT bloated with too many features. This makes it easy for anyone to create a slider, regardless of their skillset.</p>\n<h3>Here’s How Smart Slider 3 Works</h3>\n<p>After installing and activating the plugin, you can head over to Smart Slider dashboard to create a new slider. You can find 2 options: New Slider and Template Library.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>New Slider</strong>: Use this option if you want to create a slider from the ground up.</li>\n<li><strong>Template Library</strong>: Use this option if you want to import a readymade slider from the library and then customize it. Not only does it save time, but it also lets you build a slider with the perfect color palette and design.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>In addition to these 2 options, you can also find a sample slider that helps you understand how Smart Slider works even before you create one for your site.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/smart-slider-3-interface.png\" alt=\"smart slider 3 interface\" width=\"740\" height=\"317\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233873\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/smart-slider-3-interface.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/smart-slider-3-interface-300x129.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>Upon clicking New Slider button, you’ll be prompted to choose a slider preset. You can specify the slider name, and width and height of your slider. Select a slider preset and click Create.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/smart-slider-3-drag-and-drop.png\" alt=\"smart slider 3 drag and drop\" width=\"740\" height=\"319\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233872\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/smart-slider-3-drag-and-drop.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/smart-slider-3-drag-and-drop-300x129.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>Next, you’ll be asked to upload images or videos for your slider. You can simply drag and drop the files and position them per your preference. As you scroll down, you’ll be shown all available customization options and instructions explaining how to publish a slider. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/smart-slider-3-interface.png\" alt=\"smart slider 3 interface\" width=\"740\" height=\"317\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233873\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/smart-slider-3-interface.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/smart-slider-3-interface-300x129.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>To preview the slider, you can click on the Preview button at the top.</p>\n<h3>Features in Smart Slider 3</h3>\n<p>Now that you know how easy it’s to build a slider from scratch with <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/smart-slider-3/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Smart Slider 3</a>, let’s take a deeper look at other features.</p>\n<p><strong>1. 180+ Slider Samples</strong>:</p>\n<p>Building a custom slider could be a tedious task especially if you’re not a designer and often end up creating mediocre graphics and slides. With a slider sample, you can rest assured that your slider always looks professional with the right color combination and elements.</p>\n<p>All you have to do is to choose the right slider sample from the library and customize it per your needs.</p>\n<p><strong>2. Easy-to-Use Interface</strong>:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/smart-slider-3-settings.png\" alt=\"smart slider 3 settings\" width=\"740\" height=\"403\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233876\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/smart-slider-3-settings.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/smart-slider-3-settings-300x163.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/smart-slider-3/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Smart Slider 3</a> makes it easy to build an eye-catching slider thanks to the easy-to-use interface.</p>\n<p>Creating a slider with this plugin is a no-brainer. Simply navigate to the <strong>Smart Slider</strong> option in the admin menu and then click on the <strong>Add Slide</strong> button.</p>\n<p>As you upload media files to the slider, you’ll be shown how to publish that slider on your posts, pages, and theme files. Just scroll down the page and you can find customization options as well.</p>\n<p>The best thing is that if you want to extensively customize the appearance of your slider, you can enable <strong>Expert</strong> mode. This will show up advanced customization options.</p>\n<p><strong>3. Build Sliders for any Purposes</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/smart-slider-3/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Smart Slider 3</a> allows you to create a slider for any purposes. A few use cases are:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Create a slideshow to showcase your portfolio</li>\n<li>Dynamically show your blog posts on homepage</li>\n<li>Display a full page slider that covers the above-the-fold area in your landing page.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Support and Pricing for Smart Slider 3</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/smart-slider-3-pricing.png\" alt=\"smart slider 3 pricing\" width=\"740\" height=\"337\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233874\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/smart-slider-3-pricing.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/smart-slider-3-pricing-300x137.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/smart-slider-3/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Smart Slider 3</a> has an extensive documentation that guides you through every aspect of building and publishing sliders on your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">WordPress site</a>. They also run a YouTube channel where they cover all Smart Slider 3 tutorials, step by step.</p>\n<p>Smart Slider 3 only offers ticket based support. You can get in touch with them via their contact form published on the support page.</p>\n<p>Best of all, with any pro license, you’ll get ALL features of Smart Slider 3. There’re 3 different pricing plans:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Single domain ($35): Obviously, for 1 site</li>\n<li>Business ($150): For 10 sites</li>\n<li>Unlimited ($250): For Unlimited sites</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Smart Slider 3 vs. Soliloquy</h3>\n<p>Both <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/smart-slider-3/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Smart Slider 3</a> and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/soliloquy/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Soliloquy</a> are 2 of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-slider-plugins-comparison/\">best slider plugins for WordPress</a>. Let’s have a head-to-head comparison between each slider, so you can decide which one is the best choice for your needs.</p>\n<p><strong>User Interface Comparison</strong>:</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/soliloquy/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Soliloquy</a> interface will make you feel like it’s a part of your native WordPress environment. On the other hand, the Smart Slider 3’s interface looks a bit different. It’s designed so as to make the slide creation process quick and easy even for beginner level users.</p>\n<p>If you want a minimalistic dashboard for your slider plugin, then you might want to check out Soliloquy.</p>\n<p>With Smart Slider 3, even though the dashboard isn’t as sleek as Soliloquy, there’s little to no learning curve to tackle for building a slider.</p>\n<p><strong>Features &amp; Pricing Comparison </strong></p>\n<p>Soliloquy comes with a lot of built-in features and addons. Conversely, Smart Slider 3 is focused on providing hundreds of slider samples, so users can quickly build a slider without having to build it from scratch.</p>\n<p>Currently, Smart Slider 3 offers 5 slider types, 23+ layer types, and 100+ sample sliders.</p>\n<p>The pricing for Soliloquy starts at $19. But the starter plan only provides you with basic features. To get full features, you’ll have to subscribe to its Developer plan for $99.</p>\n<p>The pricing for Smart Slider 3 starts at $35. With $35, you’ll get all features of this plugin and automatic updates for lifetime.</p>\n<h3>Our Verdict on Smart Slider 3</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/smart-slider-3/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Smart Slider 3</a> is the best choice for users who want an easy-to-use slider plugin that comes with tons of readymade slider templates. For $35, you can purchase a pro version that offers all available features.</p>\n<p>Plus, all sliders are 100% responsive, meaning they’ll look good on phone, tablet, and computer.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you decide whether Smart Slider 3 is the best choice for your website.</p>\n<p>If you enjoyed this article, you might also want to check out our <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/soliloquy/\">review on Soliloquy plugin</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/smart-slider-3/\">Smart Slider 3 Review (2019): Is It Better Than Soliloquy?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/smart-slider-3/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml