al Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10800:\"<p>Are you looking for the best Divi child themes?</p>\n<p>Elegant Themes offers two different flavors of Divi: Divi Theme and Divi Builder. While Divi Theme is a highly customizable WordPress theme, Divi Builder is a drag and drop page builder plugin that works with any WordPress theme.  </p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share some of the best Divi child themes you can try on your website.</p>\n<h3>What is the Difference Between a Divi Child Theme and a Divi Layout?</h3>\n<p>A Divi child theme is a WordPress theme that inherits all the functionalities and styling of <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Divi core theme</a>. </p>\n<p>It allows you to customize a pre-built design that works on top of the Divi Builder. Using a Divi child theme is highly recommended if you want to customize function, styles, and design of your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-themes/divi-theme-review/\" title=\"Divi Theme &#038; Builder Review: Is It Worth the Price?\">Divi Theme</a>.</p>\n<p>The benefit is that with a child theme, all theme customizations will be preserved even after you update your core Divi Theme.</p>\n<p>On the other hand, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-divi-layouts/\" title=\"11 Best Divi Layouts and Supported Themes for Divi Builder\">Divi Layouts</a> are simple templates that you can use with the Divi Builder plugin to design your website. These layouts can be customized using the drag and drop page builder.</p>\n<p>You can also use the Divi Builder to create your own custom Divi layouts. The Builder allows you to import and export the theme layouts between WordPress websites. Here are some of the best Divi child themes that you can use.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/design-space-artisan-e-commerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Artisan\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. Artisan</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/design-space-artisan-e-commerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Artisan\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/artisan.jpg\" alt=\"Artisan\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-231175\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/artisan.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/artisan-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/artisan-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Artisan is an eCommerce-based child theme for the Divi WordPress theme. This Divi child theme&#8217;s layout is perfect for food bloggers, photographers, creative artists, small businesses, and any type of online store. It has 6 custom page layouts, stylish image galleries, and more. It integrates with popular payment methods including PayPal, credit card payments, etc.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://aspengrovestudios.com/product/fashion-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Fashion\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Fashion</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://aspengrovestudios.com/product/fashion-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Fashion\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/fashion.jpg\" alt=\"Fashion\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-231178\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/fashion.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/fashion-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/fashion-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Fashion is a 1-page Divi child theme built specifically for fashion designers, models, fashion shows, and other fashion-based businesses. It can be used to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/start-a-fashion-website/\" title=\"How To Start a Fashion Website with WordPress &#038; Make Money\">create a fashion website</a>. It has parallax scrolling for refined user experience. This theme comes with beautiful colors and slider ribbons for decorating your website. Fashion is shipped with lightbox photo galleries and is compatible with WooCommerce to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-an-online-store-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Create an Online Store – Step by Step (with Pictures)\">start an online store</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/design-space-flora/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Flora\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Flora</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/design-space-flora/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Flora\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/flora.jpg\" alt=\"Flora\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-231179\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/flora.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/flora-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/flora-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Flora is an elegant Divi child theme. It has 12 custom page layouts including the homepage and blog page. This theme is made for fine arts, photography, and other artistic websites. It has a grid-based homepage with built-in sections to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/add-portfolio-wordpress-site-beginners-guide/\" title=\"How to Add a Portfolio to Your WordPress Site: Beginner’s Guide\">display your portfolio</a>. Flora comes with 3 portfolio styles: slider, lightbox, and full-width. It has free Google fonts support for stylish typography.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://aspengrovestudios.com/product/interior-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Interior\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. Interior</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://aspengrovestudios.com/product/interior-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Interior\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/interior.jpg\" alt=\"Interior\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-231181\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/interior.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/interior-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/interior-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for a Divi child theme to create a website for your interior designing business, then Interior Divi is the right choice. You can use the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\" title=\"7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders Compared\">drag and drop builder</a> to easily add features on your website. It comes with a large homepage header with a scroll down button, large images on each page, parallax scrolling, a text combined photos section, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/be-superfly-josefin/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Josefin\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. Josefin</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/be-superfly-josefin/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Josefin\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/josefin.jpg\" alt=\"Josefin\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-231183\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/josefin.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/josefin-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/josefin-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Josefin is a modern, multipurpose Divi child theme. It has over 8 custom page layouts, 25 Divi library layouts, homepage sections, modules, and unique responsive elements. The Josefin&#8217;s design features a fullscreen parallax header, videos section, and parallax ribbons. This Divi child theme comes with Twitter and Instagram feed integration to connect your social media audience with your website. Josefin is compatible with the Font Awesome package and WooCommerce.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/design-space-soho/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Soho\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Soho</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/design-space-soho/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Soho\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/soho.jpg\" alt=\"Soho\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-231173\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/soho.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/soho-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/soho-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Soho is an eye-catching Divi child theme built for photographers, bloggers, and creative artists. It&#8217;s built on top of the Divi theme for better speed and performance. It includes 11 Divi library layouts with 4 image gallery options. It has a fullscreen homepage slider and parallax scrolling for better user experience. Soho child theme supports Google Fonts throughout the website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/zara-divi-child-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Zara\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Zara</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/zara-divi-child-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Zara\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/zara.jpg\" alt=\"Zara\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-231163\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/zara.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/zara-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/zara-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Zara is a premium restaurant-based Divi child theme with amazing features and beautiful colors. It comes with animation effects, the Master Slider Pro plugin, a custom restaurant menu page template, and a special menu slider. It features multiple reservation forms for users to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-booking-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Booking Plugins Compared\">make bookings</a> and reservations. Zara offers easy customization options, responsive design, and a 1-click demo import.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find the best Divi child theme for your needs. You may also want to check out our guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/install-setup-wordpress-multisite-network/\" title=\"How to Install and Set Up WordPress Multisite Network\">how to install and set up a WordPress multisite network</a> and read our complete comparison between <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/divi-vs-avada/\" title=\"Divi vs. Avada: Which Theme is BEST for You? (Compared)\">Divi vs Avada</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-divi-child-themes/\">7 Best Divi Child Themes for a Highly Customized Website</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-divi-child-themes/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n		