r <strong>WPForms Affiliate Challenge</strong> and we have some <strong>mind-blowing prizes</strong> up for grabs.</p>\n<p>Why an affiliate giveaway? WPForms is growing like crazy and we&#8217;re super excited about it! We want to share that excitement and continue to spread the word so we can help <strong>even more</strong> website owners grow their businesses online.</p>\n<p>Here&#8217;s how you can win&#8230;</p>\n<h3>How to Join the WPForms Affiliate Challenge</h3>\n<p>WPForms affiliate partners will have the chance to win some epic prizes based on their total number of WPForms sales in <strong>June 2019</strong>.</p>\n<p>All affiliates will be <strong>automatically entered into the giveaway</strong>, so all you need to do is sign up and start sharing your special affiliate link:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"btn btn-block\" style=\"background-color: #e27730 !important; color: #fff !important; padding: 15px 25px !important; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px !important; -moz-border-radius: 4px !important; -webkit-border-radius: 4px !important; font-weight: bold;\" title=\"Click here to join our affiliate program\" href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/shareasale.cfm?merchantID=64312\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Click Here to Join Our Affiliate Program</a></p>\n<p>For detailed instructions on how to sign up and start sharing your link, see our <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/affiliates/\">WPForms Affiliates page</a>.</p>\n<h3>What You Could Win:</h3>\n<p><strong>Amazon Echo (valued at $75) &#8211; 10 Sales</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-476939\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/amazon-echo-affiliate-prize.jpg\" alt=\"amazon echo affiliate prize\" width=\"562\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/amazon-echo-affiliate-prize.jpg 562w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/amazon-echo-affiliate-prize-300x160.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" /></p>\n<p>If you get 10 sales, you&#8217;ll win an Amazon Echo. Play music, ask about the weather, make calls, send and receive messages, get news, and more —just by asking your new best friend, Alexa.</p>\n<p><strong>Apple Watch (valued at $400) &#8211; 25 Sales</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-476938\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/affiliate-post-apple-watch.jpg\" alt=\"affiliate post - apple watch\" width=\"562\" height=\"301\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/affiliate-post-apple-watch.jpg 562w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/affiliate-post-apple-watch-300x161.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" /></p>\n<p>A beautiful display for a revolutionized workout experience. Stream a podcast while your watch tells you everything about your movements and body. Maybe it tells the future, too. It <strong>is</strong> Apple, after all. 😉</p>\n<p><strong>iPhone XS (valued at $1,000) &#8211; 50 Sales</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-476950\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/iphone-xs-affiliate-prize.png\" alt=\"iphone xs affiliate prize\" width=\"562\" height=\"335\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/iphone-xs-affiliate-prize.png 562w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/iphone-xs-affiliate-prize-300x179.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" /></p>\n<p>A stunning edge-to-edge display. Professional looking selfies with Depth Control. But you <strong>know </strong>the first thing you’ll do with your new iPhone XS is use the Face ID tech to text your friends as a talking unicorn head. We get it.</p>\n<p><strong>iMac 4K (valued at $1,499) &#8211; 75 Sales</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-476953\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/affiliate-post-imac-4k.jpg\" alt=\"affiliate post - imac 4k\" width=\"562\" height=\"317\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/affiliate-post-imac-4k.jpg 562w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/affiliate-post-imac-4k-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" /></p>\n<p>A sparkling 4K display with lightning fast performance. Perfect for video editing, gaming, and stirring up some serious computer envy from your friends.</p>\n<p><strong>Full Body Massage Chair (valued at $2,500) &#8211; 100 Sales</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-476954\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/affiliate-challenge-prize.jpg\" alt=\"affiliate challenge prize\" width=\"562\" height=\"453\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/affiliate-challenge-prize.jpg 562w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/affiliate-challenge-prize-300x242.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" /></p>\n<p>Imagine your new daily zen routine of a zero-gravity massage complete with heat and premium Bluetooth speakers. After kicking so much butt with 100 affiliates sales, you’ll <strong>deserve</strong> to relax just like the elite do.</p>\n<p><strong>Bali Vacation (valued at $5,000) &#8211; 250 sales</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-476955\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/affiliate-challenge-bali-trip-1.jpg\" alt=\"affiliate challenge bali trip\" width=\"562\" height=\"374\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/affiliate-challenge-bali-trip-1.jpg 562w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/affiliate-challenge-bali-trip-1-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" /></p>\n<p>We’ll cover your flight and accommodations to Bali so you can bask in the luxury of a lush villa nestled on a pristine beach. Don’t forget to send us pics of the iconic rice paddies and lively beach bars, too.</p>\n<p><strong>Hawai’i Vacation (valued at $10,000) &#8211; 500 sales</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-476959\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/affiliate-challenge-oahu-trip-1.jpg\" alt=\"affiliate challenge oahu trip\" width=\"562\" height=\"343\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/affiliate-challenge-oahu-trip-1.jpg 562w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/affiliate-challenge-oahu-trip-1-300x183.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" /></p>\n<p>Take an unforgettable trip on us to Hawai’i. Revel in all the amazing nightlife, alluring beaches, and mouthwatering seafood Oahu has to offer.</p>\n<p><strong>Fiji Vacation (valued at $16,000) &#8211; 1000 sales</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-476960\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/affiliate-challenge-fiji-trip-1.jpg\" alt=\"affiliate-challenge-fiji-trip\" width=\"562\" height=\"342\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/affiliate-challenge-fiji-trip-1.jpg 562w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/affiliate-challenge-fiji-trip-1-300x183.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" /></p>\n<p>And if you hit 1,000 sales, you’ll get our grand prize! You’ll be whisked away to enjoy the soft white sand beaches and decadence of an all-inclusive resort in Fiji.</p>\n<p>Are you ready to get this challenge started? Who couldn’t use a new tech toy or luxury beachside vacation—especially if you’re not the one footing the bill!</p>\n<h3>How the WPForms Affiliate Challenge Works</h3>\n<p><strong>1. Sign Up as a WPForms Affiliate</strong></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re not an affiliate yet, you need to become one. Don’t worry, it’s really easy. All you need to do is<a href=\"https://www.shareasale.com/shareasale.cfm?merchantID=64312\"> sign up for the program</a>.</p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re already an affiliate, you&#8217;re automatically entered in this challenge!</p>\n<p><strong>2. Promote WPForms</strong></p>\n<p>Once you&#8217;re signed up as an affiliate, <strong>start promoting WPForms</strong>.</p>\n<p>Here are some tips on the best ways to get more sales:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Write a blog post.</strong> You could write 1 post or a series, covering<a href=\"https://wpforms.com/features/\"> different features</a> of the WPForms plugin. Try picking your favorite<a href=\"https://wpforms.com/features/\"> feature or addon</a> and embedding the feature&#8217;s video into your post for a great visual.</li>\n<li><strong>Send an email blast.</strong> Pick your favorite way to use WPForms and send an email to your subscriber list telling them about it.<a href=\"https://wpforms.com/addons/conversational-forms-addon/\"> Conversational Forms</a> or the<a href=\"https://wpforms.com/addons/surveys-and-polls-addon/\"> Survey and Polls Addon</a> are a couple of our favorites.</li>\n<li><strong>Recommend WPForms to your clients</strong>. Never underestimate the power of word-of-mouth marketing!</li>\n<li><strong>Add WPForms to your Recommended page on your website. </strong>A recommended page on a website is a popular spot that visitors love to check out to see what tools you&#8217;re using, and it&#8217;s a great place for affiliate links. Try adding the page at the beginning or the end of your primary menu.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>3. Earn Sales</strong></p>\n<p>The more sales you earn, the better the prize!</p>\n<p>During the challenge period, each sale will go towards your chance to win one of the big prizes, but don’t forget that <strong>you&#8217;ll also be making money on each of your sales</strong> with our<a href=\"https://wpforms.com/affiliates/\"> affiliate program</a>, during and after the challenge period.</p>\n<p>Winners of the WPForms Affiliate Challenge will be notified via email and will get their prizes in August.</p>\n<p>So what are you waiting for?<a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/shareasale.cfm?merchantID=64312\"> Sign up for the WPForms Affiliate Program today</a> and start earning money right away while